title: [PSP]GPSP Game Boy advance Emulator 08, with gba bios included
description:
This is currently the best GBA emulator, and you don\\\&#039;t have to search pages for the bios either, as it is included in this package. Source is included.

Unpack the zip file and copy the gpsp08 folder to your psp\\\&#039;s GAME folder, and launch it. If you got a 2.0+ firmware you will need to get some kind of loader, or downgrade.

As for firmware 1.5, simply copy the gpsp08 and gpsp08% from the gpsp15 folder in the package and place it into your psp\\\&#039;s GAME folder.

PS! you still gotta download roms.
